<p class="mb-0">ou, para sites hospedados no Squarespace:</p>
<a href=<%="https://" + current_shop.domain + "/scripts/aplicatify-serviceworker.js"%>><%= current_shop.domain + "/scripts/aplicatify-serviceworker.js"%></a>
<p></p>
